data.description: Experience eco-friendly luxury in this 4-bed, 3-bath home featuring solar panels, a 3-car garage, and a landscaped front yard. The open, split floor plan is highlighted by recessed lighting, abundant natural light, sleek tile flooring, and a cozy fireplace. The upgraded kitchen has quartz counters, a subway tile backsplash, SS appliances, cabinets with crown moulding, a pantry, an island with pendant lighting, and a breakfast bar. An additional loft with storage leads to the 4th bedroom. The main bedroom is a soft carpeted retreat, complete with an ensuite with dual vanities, an extended shower, and a walk-in closet. Outside, relax on a covered patio overlooking a lush lawn. The seller boosts the appeal with an offer of $10,000 towards closing costs or rate buy down. See it now!
